      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Formal equivalency mapping between validation and COU input parameters not required at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "The validation and COU configurations share the same pump geometry and operating envelope. Formal input-parameter equivalency analysis is not required at MRL 2; qualitative similarity was confirmed by engineering review."
    }
