    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 for a Class II device with medium model influence. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions within the defined COU. Acceptance is recorded on the basis that the primary requirement (RH < 1.0) is satisfied at all five operating points.",
